SELECT PopulationHealthData.population_name, PopulationHealthData.population_density, DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_name FROM PopulationHealthData JOIN DiseaseOutbreaks ON PopulationHealthData.population_id = DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id WHERE DiseaseOutbreaks.environmental_factor = 'Air Pollution' ORDER BY PopulationHealthData.population_name ASC;

SELECT DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_name, EnvironmentalFactors.factor_name, PopulationHealthData.population_health_status FROM DiseaseOutbreaks JOIN EnvironmentalFactors ON DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id = EnvironmentalFactors.factor_id JOIN PopulationHealthData ON DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id = PopulationHealthData.population_id WHERE PopulationHealthData.population_health_status = 'Healthy' ORDER BY DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_name ASC, EnvironmentalFactors.factor_name DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id, DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_name, EnvironmentalFactors.factor_name, PopulationHealthData.population_name FROM DiseaseOutbreaks JOIN EnvironmentalFactors ON DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id = EnvironmentalFactors.factor_id JOIN PopulationHealthData ON DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id = PopulationHealthData.population_id WHERE DiseaseOutbreaks.disease_id BETWEEN 1 AND 3 ORDER BY PopulationHealthData.population_name DESC;
